1115	   `.thread-welcome*` so the file's intro tokens (used by Tide's
1116	   marketing demo) don't accidentally clash. */
1117	.thread-welcome {
1118	  text-align: center;
1119	  color: var(--ink-mute);
1120	  padding: 64px 0 40px;
1121	  font-size: 13.5px;
1122	}
