1667	/* =============================================================
1668	   MOBILE — slide-over sidebar (Task 27).
1669	   At <= 720px, the sidebar lifts off the page flow and slides in over
1670	   the chat. Width override (280px !important) wins over the desktop
1671	   collapsed-rail width (56px) so even if the user collapsed on
1672	   desktop and then resized to mobile, the slide-over is full-width.
1673	   The composer goes edge-to-edge. The hamburger toggle replaces the
1674	   collapse toggle. The scrim catches taps to close.
1675	   ============================================================= */
1676	
1677	@media (max-width: 720px) {
